#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:29
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook; is a very complicated program with lots of built-in features. "
"Some of the more advanced features of &kaddressbook; are documented in this "
"appendix, primarily to keep the main document from getting too large and "
"unwieldy."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook; je zelo zapleten program z veliko vgrajenimi funkcijami. V "
"tem dodatku so dokumentirane nekatere naprednejše funkcije programa "
"&kaddressbook;, predvsem zato, da glavni dokument ne bi postal preobsežen in "
"nepregleden."

