#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:124
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> function lets you tailor a "
"hard-copy of your address book data just about any way you want."
msgstr ""
"funkcija <quote>Predogled za tiskanje</quote> v programu &kaddressbook; vam "
"omogoča, da prilagodite tiskano kopijo podatkov iz imenika na poljuben način."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:129 docbook-reference.docbook:205
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> "
"dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled tiskanja</"
"quote> storitve &kaddressbook;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:135 docbook-reference.docbook:163
#: docbook-reference.docbook:211
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> dialog."
"</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote> "
"storitve &kaddressbook;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:138
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> dialog. You may select one or "
"more entire address books, or just a smattering of individual contacts."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote>. Izberete "
"lahko enega ali več celotnih imenikov ali le nekaj posameznih stikov."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:147
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first step is to select the contacts to be included in the printout. If "
"you wish to print just a smattering of individual contacts, you must choose "
"the contacts to be printed before invoking the "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Print Preview</guisubmenu></menuchoice> dialog. If you "
"wish to select all your contacts, or all the contacts in a particular "
"address book, you can do it here. Click "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-next.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Next</guibutton> when "
"you have made your selection. A new screen will appear."
msgstr ""
"Najprej je treba izbrati stike, ki bodo vključeni v izpis. Če želite "
"natisniti le nekaj posameznih stikov, morate izbrati stike, ki jih želite "
"natisniti, preden sprožite pogovorno okno "
"<menuchoice><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-preview-archive.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Predogled tiskanja</guisubmenu></menuchoice>. Če želite "
"izbrati vse stike ali vse stike v določenem imeniku, lahko to storite tukaj. "
"Kliknite <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-"
"next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Naprej</"
"guibutton>, ko ste izbrali. Prikazalo se bo novo okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:157
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> dialog."
msgstr ""
"Drugi posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote> v "
"&kaddressbook;."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:166
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The second screen in &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> dialog. "
"You may choose a sort field and a sort direction (up or down). You may also "
"choose among seven different print layouts."
msgstr ""
"Drugi posnetek zaslona v pogovornem oknu <quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote> v "
"programu &kaddressbook;. Izberete lahko polje razvrščanja in smer "
"razvrščanja (navzgor ali navzdol). Izbirate lahko tudi med sedmimi "
"različnimi postavitvami tiskanja."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:175
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here you can choose a sort field (any one of the 47 named fields in the "
"contact record), the direction of the sort, and any one of seven different "
"report formats. When you click <guibutton> "
"<inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"go-next.png\" format="
"\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Next</guibutton>, you will be "
"given a chance to tailor the color scheme to be used."
msgstr ""
"Tu lahko izberete polje za razvrščanje (katero koli od 47 poimenovanih polj "
"v zapisu stika), smer razvrščanja in eno od sedmih različnih oblik poročila. "
"Ko kliknete <guibutton> <inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"go-next.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject> </inlinemediaobject>Naprej</"
"guibutton>, boste lahko prilagodili barvno shemo, ki se bo uporabila."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:183
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</"
"quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Tretji posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled "
"tiskanja</quote> v &kaddressbook;.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:189
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A third screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> "
"dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Tretji posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled tiskanja</"
"quote> v &kaddressbook;.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:192
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The third screen in &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> dialog. "
"You may select a color scheme here."
msgstr ""
"Tretji posnetek zaslona pogovornega okna <quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote> v "
"&kaddressbook;. Tu lahko izberete barvno shemo."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:201
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a picture of the completed report. It is now ready for printing."
msgstr "Tukaj je slika dokončanega poročila. Zdaj je pripravljen za tiskanje."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:214
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Print Preview</quote> after the report has been "
"generated and is ready to print. You may select alternative print "
"orientations (landscape or portrait) and launch the print task from this "
"window."
msgstr ""
"<quote>Predogled tiskanja</quote>, ko je poročilo ustvarjeno in pripravljeno "
"za tiskanje. V tem oknu lahko izberete različne usmeritve tiskanja (ležeče "
"ali pokončno) in zaženete opravilo tiskanja."

#. Tag: title
#: docbook-reference.docbook:229
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Configure LDAP Dialog"
msgstr "Pogovorno okno Konfiguracija LDAP"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:231
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Here is a picture of the first configuration screen that appears when you "
"choose either the <guibutton>Configure LDAP Servers...</guibutton> button in "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Import&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import from LDAP Server...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> dialog or the <menuchoice><guimenu>Settings</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> <imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Configure &kaddressbook;...</guisubmenu></menuchoice> menu "
"item."
msgstr ""
"Tukaj je slika prvega konfiguracijskega zaslona, ki se prikaže, ko izberete "
"tipko <guibutton>Konfiguriraj LDAP Strežnike...</guibutton> v "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu> <guisubmenu>Uvoz&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi iz LDAP Strežnika...</guimenuitem> </"
"menuchoice> pogovorni vrstici ali element menija &kaddressbook;..."
"<menuchoice><guimenu>Nastavitve</guimenu><guisubmenu><inlinemediaobject> "
"<imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"configure.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></"
"imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Konfiguriraj </guisubmenu></menuchoice>."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:240
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP Server</"
"quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Zaslonska slika &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:246
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP Server</"
"quote> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Zaslonska slika &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:249
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP Server</quote> dialog after choosing "
"the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import from LDAP Server...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> function and left clicking the <guibutton>Configure LDAP "
"Servers...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo <quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote> pogovorno okno "
"po izbiri funkcije <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi iz "
"LDAP strežnika...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> in levem kliku na "
"<guibutton>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnike...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:259
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you have already configured one or more <acronym>LDAP</acronym> servers, "
"use this screen to select the servers that should be queried when you search "
"for a name or email address. Use the <guibutton>Add host...</guibutton> "
"button to add a new server to the list of available <acronym>LDAP</acronym> "
"hosts. Use the <guibutton>Edit host...</guibutton> button to reconfigure a "
"server that's already on the list, and the <guibutton>Remove host</"
"guibutton> button to delete an entry you don't need any more. The "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"edit-undo.png"
"\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></inlinemediaobject>Reset</guibutton> "
"button can be used to undo the last <quote>Add</quote> or <quote>Remove</"
"quote> action performed. The <quote>Defaults</quote> button is inoperative "
"in release 5.10.3. The rest of the buttons (OK, Apply, Cancel) have their "
"ordinary functions: apply changes and exit, apply changes and stay here, and "
"exit the dialog without making any changes, respectively."
msgstr ""
"Če ste že konfigurirali enega ali več strežnikov <acronym>LDAP</acronym>, na "
"tem zaslonu izberite strežnike, po katerih naj se poizveduje pri iskanju "
"imena ali e-poštnega naslova. Z gumbom <guibutton>Dodaj gostitelja...</"
"guibutton> dodajte nov strežnik na seznam razpoložljivih gostiteljev "
"<acronym>LDAP</acronym>. Z gumbom <guibutton>Uredi gostitelja...</guibutton> "
"lahko znova konfigurirate strežnik, ki je že na seznamu, z gumbom "
"<guibutton>Odstrani gostitelja</guibutton> pa izbrišete vnos, ki ga ne "
"potrebujete več. Gumb <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata "
"fileref=\"edit-undo.png\" format=\"PNG\"/></imageobject></"
"inlinemediaobject>Ponastavi</guibutton> lahko uporabite za razveljavitev "
"zadnjega opravljenega dejanja <quote>Dodaj</quote> ali <quote>Odstrani</"
"quote>. Gumb <quote>Privzete nastavitve</quote> v izdaji 5.10.3 ne deluje. "
"Preostali gumbi (OK, Uveljavi, Prekliči) imajo običajne funkcije: uporabi "
"spremembe in izstopi, uporabi spremembe in ostani tukaj ter izstopi iz "
"pogovornega okna, ne da bi opravil kakršne koli spremembe."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:271
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose either the <guibutton>Add host...</guibutton> button or the "
"<guibutton>Edit host...</guibutton> button, the following dialog will appear."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete gumb <guibutton>Dodaj gostitelja...</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Uredi gostitelja...</guibutton>, se prikaže naslednje pogovorno "
"okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:276
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP "
"Server</quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Drug posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:282
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP "
"Server</quote> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Drug posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:285
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Configure LDAP Server</quote> dialog after left "
"clicking either the <guibutton>Add Host...</guibutton> or the "
"<guibutton>Edit Host...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo <quote>Konfiguriraj LDAP strežnik</quote> pogovorno okno "
"po levem kliku na <guibutton>Dodaj gostitelja...</guibutton> ali "
"<guibutton>Uredi gostitelja...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:294
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"The first four fields (<quote>User:</quote>, <quote>Bind DN:</quote>, "
"<quote>Realm:</quote>, and <quote>Password:</quote>) will all be grayed out "
"unless authentication is required. Obtain these credentials from the LDAP "
"server's administrator. Enter the appropriate &URI; in the <quote>Host:</"
"quote> field. The default values for <quote>Port:</quote>, <quote>Size limit:"
"</quote>, &etc; will work OK for most users. You can use the "
"<guibutton>Query Server</guibutton> button to set up the <quote>DN:</quote> "
"field. I have no idea what the <quote>Filter:</quote> field is for. If you "
"figure it out, please let me know (davidbryant AT gvtc.com)."
msgstr ""
"Prva štiri polja (<quote>Uporabnik:</quote>, <quote>Razločevalno ime DN:</"
"quote>, <quote>Področje:</quote> in <quote>Geslo:</quote>) bodo vsa siva, "
"razen če je potrebna overovitev. Te poverilnice pridobite od skrbnika "
"strežnika LDAP. V polje <quote>Host:</quote> vnesite ustrezen &URI;. "
"Privzete vrednosti za <quote>Vrata:</quote>, <quote>Omejitev velikosti:</"
"quote>, &etc; bodo za večino uporabnikov delovale v redu. Za nastavitev "
"polja <quote>DN:</quote> lahko uporabite gumb <guibutton>Poizvedovalni "
"strežnik</guibutton>. Nimam pojma, čemu je namenjeno polje <quote>Filter:</"
"quote>. Če boste to ugotovili, mi to sporočite (davidbryant AT gvtc.com)."

# schmear?
#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:301
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <quote>Security</quote> section to specify the encryption method to "
"use: <quote>No</quote> for an unencrypted connection, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-tls\"><acronym>TLS</acronym></glossterm> for Transport Layer "
"Security, or <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ssl\"><acronym>SSL</acronym></"
"glossterm> for Secure Socket Layer. Use the <quote>Authentication</quote> "
"options to specify what level of authentication the server requires: "
"<quote>Anonymous</quote> for no name or password at all, <quote>Simple</"
"quote> if <quote>Bind DN</quote> and <quote>Password</quote> must be given, "
"and <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-sasl\"><acronym>SASL</acronym></glossterm> "
"(Simple Authentication and Security Layer) for the whole schmear (four data "
"items). If <quote>SASL</quote> is chosen, use the <guibutton>Query Server</"
"guibutton> button to set the advanced options for this host."
msgstr ""
"V razdelku <quote>Varnost</quote> določite metodo šifriranja, ki jo želite "
"uporabiti: <quote>Ne</quote> za nešifrirano povezavo, <glossterm linkend="
"\"gloss-tls\"><acronym>TLS</acronym></glossterm> za Transport Layer Security "
"ali <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-ssl\"><acronym>SSL</acronym></glossterm> za "
"Secure Socket Layer. Z možnostmi <quote>Overitev</quote> določite, katero "
"raven overitve zahteva strežnik: <quote>Anonimno</quote> za sploh brez imena "
"ali gesla, <quote>Preprosto</quote>, če je treba navesti <quote>Vezni DN</"
"quote> in <quote>Geslo</quote>, ter <glossterm linkend=\"gloss-sasl"
"\"><acronym>SASL</acronym></glossterm> (Simple Authentication and Security "
"Layer) za celoten schmear (štiri podatkovne elemente). Če je izbrana možnost "
"<quote>SASL</quote>, z gumbom <guibutton>Poizvedovalni strežnik</guibutton> "
"nastavite napredne možnosti za tega gostitelja."

#. Tag: title
#: docbook-reference.docbook:317
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Import CSV File Function"
msgstr "Funkcija za uvoz datoteke CSV"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:319
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you choose the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Import "
"CSV file...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function, you will be presented with "
"a dialog. After you click the "
"<guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref=\"document-"
"open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></guibutton> "
"button and choose the file to be imported, the screen will look like this."
msgstr ""
"Ko izberete funkcijo <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu> <guimenuitem>Uvozi "
"CSV datoteko...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se prikaže pogovorno okno. Ko "
"kliknete gumb <guibutton><inlinemediaobject><imageobject><imagedata fileref="
"\"document-open.png\" format=\"PNG\"/> </imageobject></inlinemediaobject></"
"guibutton> in izberete datoteko za uvoz, bo zaslon videti takole."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:327
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</quote> "
"dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Uvoz CSV datoteke</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:333
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</quote> "
"dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna <quote>Uvoz "
"CSV datoteke</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:336
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</quote> dialog after choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import CSV file...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"function and selecting the file to be imported."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Uvozi CSV datoteko</quote> po izbiri "
"funkcije <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp; "
"&nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi CSV datoteko...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> in izbiri datoteke za uvoz."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:345
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Use the <quote>Delimiter</quote> section of this dialog to specify which "
"separator character defines the end of a field in the chosen input file. If "
"quote marks are used to delimit fields with embedded separator characters, "
"you may specify the style (single or double quote) used via the <quote>Text "
"quote:</quote> drop-down box. If the input file contains dates, use the "
"<quote>Date format:</quote> field to define the way dates have been encoded. "
"The default is yyyy-mm-dd. If that's the wrong format, hover your cursor "
"over the <quote>Date format:</quote> box and a handy set of formatting "
"instructions will be displayed. If the input file is not UTF-8 encoded, use "
"the <quote>Text codec:</quote> drop-down box to specify the binary encoding "
"scheme to use. If the first row of the file contains column headers, check "
"the <quote>Skip first row of file</quote> box to avoid importing the column "
"headers as data. Use the <quote>Undefined</quote> boxes at the top of each "
"column to specify which data fields are to be imported, and where they "
"should be stored, as shown below."
msgstr ""
"Z razdelkom <quote>Razmejilnik</quote> tega pogovornega okna določite, "
"kateri ločilni znak določa konec polja v izbrani vhodni datoteki. Če se "
"narekovaji uporabljajo za razmejitev polj z vstavljenimi ločilnimi znaki, "
"lahko prek spustnega polja <quote>Citiranje besedila:</quote> določite "
"uporabljeni slog (enojni ali dvojni narekovaj). Če vhodna datoteka vsebuje "
"datume, uporabite polje <quote>Oblika datuma:</quote> za določitev načina "
"kodiranja datumov. Privzeta vrednost je llll-mm-dd. Če je to napačna oblika, "
"se s kazalcem pomaknite nad polje <quote>Oblika datuma:</quote> in prikazala "
"se bodo priročna navodila za oblikovanje. Če vhodna datoteka ni kodirana v "
"UTF-8, s spustnim poljem <quote>Kodek za besedilo:</quote> določite shemo "
"binarnega kodiranja, ki naj se uporabi. Če prva vrstica datoteke vsebuje "
"glave stolpcev, potrdite polje <quote>Preskoči prvo vrstico datoteke</"
"quote>, da se izognete uvozu glav stolpcev kot podatkov. S polji "
"<quote>Nedoločeno</quote> na vrhu vsakega stolpca določite, katera "
"podatkovna polja se bodo uvozila in kam naj se shranijo, kot je prikazano "
"spodaj."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:357
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</"
"quote> dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Drug posnetek &kaddressbook;ovega zaslona pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Uvozi CSV datoteko</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:363
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A second screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</"
"quote> dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Drug posnetek &kaddressbook;ovega zaslona pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Uvozi CSV datoteko</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:366
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Import CSV File</quote> dialog after choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Import&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Import CSV file...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"function, selecting the file to be imported, and beginning to define the "
"fields to be imported."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Uvozi CSV Datoteko</quote> po izbiri "
"funkcije <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Uvozi&nbsp; "
"&nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Uvozi CSV datoteko...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice>, izbiri datoteke za uvoz in začetku določanja polj za uvoz."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:376
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you wish the contents of the current column to be imported, choose a "
"destination from the list of field names appearing beneath the blue "
"<quote>Undefined</quote> box. See <link linkend=\"export-csv-data\">the next "
"section</link> for a list of the pre-defined fields. Use the horizontal "
"scrollbar near the bottom of the dialog to view all the columns in the input "
"file. When your selections are complete, click the <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;"
"OK&nbsp;</guibutton> button. If you have defined multiple address books, you "
"will be asked to specify which address book is to be used. &kaddressbook; "
"will then import the selected data as new contacts."
msgstr ""
"Če želite uvoziti vsebino trenutnega stolpca, izberite ciljno mesto s "
"seznama imen polj, ki se prikaže pod modrim poljem <quote>Nedoločeno</"
"quote>. Za seznam vnaprej določenih polj glejte <link linkend=\"export-csv-"
"data\">v naslednjem razdelku</link>. Za ogled vseh stolpcev v vhodni "
"datoteki uporabite vodoravno drsno vrstico na dnu pogovornega okna. Ko so "
"izbire končane, kliknite gumb <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>. "
"Če ste določili več imenikov, boste morali določiti, kateri imenik naj se "
"uporabi. &kaddressbook; bo nato uvozil izbrane podatke kot nove stike."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:382
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"If you intend to import additional datasets in the same format sometime in "
"the future, you may click the <guibutton>Save template...</guibutton> button "
"(cf. the first illustration in this section) to save the selections you have "
"made. You will be prompted to give the template a name. Later, when you "
"import another file with the same layout, you can save time by clicking the "
"<guibutton>Apply template...</guibutton> button."
msgstr ""
"Če nameravate kdaj v prihodnosti uvoziti dodatne podatkovne nize v istem "
"formatu, lahko kliknete gumb <guibutton>Shrani predlogo...</guibutton> (glej "
"prvo sliko v tem razdelku), da shranite opravljene izbire. Pozvan bo poziv "
"za poimenovanje predloge. Kasneje, ko boste uvozili drugo datoteko z enako "
"postavitvijo, lahko prihranite čas s klikom na gumb <guibutton>Apply "
"template...</guibutton>."

#. Tag: title
#: docbook-reference.docbook:391
#, no-c-format
msgid "The Export CSV File Function"
msgstr "Funkcija Izvoz CSV datoteke"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:393
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"When you invoke the <menuchoice><guimenu>File</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export "
"CSV file ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> function, a dialog box appears."
msgstr ""
"Ko prikličete funkcijo <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</"
"guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp;&nbsp;&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Izvoz CSV "
"datoteke...</guimenuitem></menuchoice>, se pojavi pogovorno okno."

#. Tag: screeninfo
#: docbook-reference.docbook:398
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<screeninfo>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Export CSV File</quote> "
"dialog.</screeninfo>"
msgstr ""
"<screeninfo>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna "
"<quote>Izvoz CSV datoteke</quote>.</screeninfo>"

#. Tag: phrase
#: docbook-reference.docbook:404
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"<phrase>A screenshot of &kaddressbook;'s <quote>Export CSV File</quote> "
"dialog.</phrase>"
msgstr ""
"<phrase>Posnetek zaslona &kaddressbook;ovega pogovornega okna <quote>Izvoz "
"CSV datoteke</quote>.</phrase>"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:407
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>Export CSV File</quote> dialog after choosing the "
"<menuchoice><guimenu>File</guimenu><guisubmenu>Export&nbsp; &nbsp;&gt;</"
"guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Export CSV file ...</guimenuitem></menuchoice> "
"function."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Izvozi CSV datoteko</quote> po "
"izbiri <menuchoice><guimenu>Datoteka</guimenu><guisubmenu>Izvoz&nbsp; &nbsp;"
"&gt;</guisubmenu><guimenuitem>Izvozi CSV datoteki...</guimenuitem></"
"menuchoice> funkcije."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:416
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"You may select all your contact data, or just a portion of it. When you "
"press the <guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton> button, you will be "
"allowed to choose the name of the generated file, and the directory in which "
"it will be written. The output file will contain the following forty-seven "
"(47) output fields, in this order, left to right. This list of field names "
"is included as the first record in the file."
msgstr ""
"Izberete lahko vse podatke o stikih ali le del podatkov. Ko pritisnete gumb "
"<guibutton>&nbsp;✔&nbsp;OK&nbsp;</guibutton>, boste lahko izbrali ime "
"ustvarjene datoteke in imenik, v katerega bo zapisana. Izhodna datoteka bo "
"vsebovala naslednjih sedeminštirideset (47) izhodnih polj v tem vrstnem redu "
"od leve proti desni. Ta seznam imen polj je vključen kot prvi zapis v "
"datoteki."

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:420
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"Formatted Name | Honorific Prefixes | Given Name | Additional Names | Family "
"Name | Honorific Suffixes | Nick Name | Birthday | Anniversary | EMail "
"(preferred) | EMail (2) | EMail (3) | EMail (4) | Home Address Street | Home "
"Address Post Office Box | Home Address City | Home Address State | Home "
"Address Zip Code | Home Address Country | Home Address Label | Business "
"Address Street | Business Address Post Office Box | Business Address City | "
"Business Address State | Business Address Zip Code | Business Address "
"Country | Business Address Label | Home Phone | Business Phone | Mobile "
"Phone | Home Fax | Business Fax | Car Phone | ISDN | Pager | Mail Client | "
"Title | Role | Organization | Note | Homepage | Blog Feed | Profession | "
"Office | Manager | Assistant | Spouse"
msgstr ""
"Formatirano ime | Častne predpone | Ime | Dodatna imena | Družinsko ime | "
"Častne pripone | Vzdevek | Rojstni dan | Obletnica | EMail (prednostno) | "
"EMail (2) | EMail (3) | EMail (4) | Ulica domačega naslova | Poštni predal "
"domačega naslova| Mesto domačega naslova | Domači naslov Država (state) | "
"Domači naslov Poštna številka | Država domačega naslova | Oznaka domačega "
"naslova | Ulica poslovnega naslova | Naslov poslovnega poštnega predal | "
"Mesto poslovnega naslova| Poslovni naslov Država (state) | Poštna številka "
"poslovnega naslova | Država domačega naslova | Oznaka domačega naslova | "
"Poslovni telefon | Mobilni telefon | Domači faks | Poslovni faks | Avto-fon "
"| ISDN | Pager | Mail Client | Naslov | Vloga | Organizacija | Opomba | "
"Domača stran | Blog Feed | Poklic | Urad | Manager | Pomočnik | Soproga"

#. Tag: para
#: docbook-reference.docbook:427
#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"All fields are formatted as character class data. Dates (Birthday and "
"Anniversary, if present) are coded as yyyy-mm-dd (Year, Month, Day)."
msgstr ""
"Vsa polja so oblikovana kot podatki znakovnega razreda. Datumi (rojstni dan "
"in obletnica, če sta prisotna) so kodirani kot llll-mm-dd (leto, mesec, dan)."

#. Tag: title
#: docbook-reference.docbook:436
