#, no-c-format
msgid ""
"&kaddressbook;'s <quote>LDAP Server Settings</quote> dialog. This dialog, "
"and its child, are documented in <link linkend=\"configure-ldap-server\">a "
"preceding section</link> of this appendix."
msgstr ""
"&kaddressbook;ovo pogovorno okno <quote>Nastavitve LDAP strežnika</quote>. "
"To pogovorno okno in njegov podrejeni del sta dokumentirana v <link linkend="
"\"configure-ldap-server\">prejšnjem razdelku</link> tega dodatka."

#. Tag: para
